       ```javascript
       function authenticateUser(req, res, next) {
         if (!req.user || !req.user.isAdmin) {
           return res.status(403).json({ error: 'Unauthorized' });
         }
         next();
       }
       ```
     - Apply it to the route:
       ```javascript
       app.put('/update-user', authenticateUser, updateUser);
       ```

